Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:37.22,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-H-GBK\fs40\c&H0A0B7D&\3c&H078F90&\bord4\frz357.4\pos(1010.667,309.904)}用高维度力量来变得受欢迎吧!!
